talon fx 8 () Status Signal Position

That error message is saying that there’s a Talon FX with ID 8 constructed on the roboRIO CAN bus; the “()” contains the CAN bus string passed into the device constructor, or an empty string if none is provided.

If the devices are all on a CANivore, make sure the CANivore name is provided to all device constructors. Additionally, make sure you are not creating multiple instances of the same device.
